interactions.flavorLineOne:
Saint-14 bows his head to you. "A fellow warrior of the Light. Come close, let me guide your path to the Lighthouse, my friend." Saint explains that to enter the Trials of Osiris, you must posess a Trials Ticket. Your ticket will track your wins and losses. Each ticket has a different powerful effect.

 Saint looks over a blank ticket. "You want as many wins as possible, obviously…" he chuckles, "but do not lose three matches, or you are done." He continues that seven wins with no losses grants access to the Lighthouse for Flawless Rewards. "I await your ascension to the Lighthouse. Good luck."

You can reset your Trials Passage on the item in your Pursuits, or on the Trials of Osiris activity node.

You approach Saint-14; the crest of his helm brims with sunlight. "You are ready. I can feel it!" He straightens his stance and looks you over.

"Guardian, the Trials of Osiris are not simply here to train you." His voice grows out of a low rolling timbre of consideration. "I am here to assess your propensity for leadership," Saint mimics a delivery reminiscent of Osiris as he speaks.

Serious now: "The Darkness is coming. The Moon is only the first glimpse. I know it." He looks into your eyes. "When it arrives, we will need heroes, leaders, as we did at the Gap, at Six Fronts." He leans in. "The others… they will look to you." Saint nods. "You will make me proud."
Saint-14 opens his arms to you when you arrive with his gift. He accepts the cookies, sets them aside, and then clasps your hand warmly. He wishes you a happy Dawning.

Saint-14 is overjoyed that you have chosen to take part in the Trials of Osiris. He tries to contain his excitement as he delivers his wonderfully rehearsed speech. Afterward, he nods and says, "I know you will give this everything, Guardian. You've never been one to hold back."

Your zeal is noted, friend, but your Light requires refinement. As the acting Officiator of the Trials of Osiris, Saint-14 has assessed the necessary requirements for entry. His assessment has set the entry bar at a measurable Power of 1010. While every Guardian has strength in their own right, some do not yet have the battle experience to operate seamlessly in a Trials fireteam.

Reach Power 1010, acquire Valor Legend rank, and defeat opponents in Elimination to participate in the Trials of Osiris.
Earn Trials engrams by competing in the Trials of Osiris and returning the tokens you earn.
Show Saint-14 proof of your deeds in the Trials of Osiris.
Earn Trials engrams by competing in the Trials of Osiris and returning the tokens you earn.
